quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  7,158,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Yemwe bantu! Mu by’ukuri njye ndi intumwa ya Allah yoherejwe kuri mwe mwese. (Allah) ni We ufite ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi. Nta yindi mana ibaho itari We, ni We utanga ubuzima akanatanga urupfu.” Bityo, nimwemere Allah n’intumwa ye ikaba n’umuhanuzi utari uzi gusoma no kwandika, we wemera Allah akanemera amagambo ye, kandi munamukurikire kugira ngo mubashe kuyoboka"
  7,159,"No mu bantu ba Musa harimo itsinda riyobora (abantu) rikoresheje ukuri, rikanagukoresha mu butabera"
  7,160,"Nuko (Abisiraheli) tubagabanyamo amoko cumi n’abiri, tunahishurira Musa ubwo abantu be bamusabaga amazi yo kunywa (tugira tuti) “Kubita inkoni yawe ku ibuye!” Nuko (arikubise) riturikamo amasoko cumi n’abiri, maze buri muryango umenya aho unywera. Twanabugamishije mu gicucu cy’igicu (igihe bayobagurikaga mu butayu bavuye mu Misiri) ndetse tunabamanurira Manu na Saluwa (tuvuga tuti) “Nimurye mu byiza twabafunguriye!” Si twe bahemukiye ahubwo ni bo ubwabo bihemukiye"
  7,161,"Munibuke ubwo babwirwaga bati “Nimuture muri uyu mudugudu (wa Yeruzalemu), hanyuma murye ibiwurimo aho mushaka hose, munavuge muti “Tubabarire ibyaha byacu”; muninjire mu marembo yawo mwicishije bugufi. “Tuzabababarira ibyaha byanyu kandi tuzongerera (ibihembo) abakora ibyiza.”"
  7,162,"Ariko bamwe muri bo bakoze ibibi, bahinduye imvugo bakora ibyo batabwiwe (aho gusaba imbabazi no kwicisha bugufi barushaho kwigomeka). Nuko tuboherereza igihano giturutse mu kirere, kubera ibikorwa bibi bakoraga"